blocks.name: STRENGTH
exercises:
5 sets [ choose weight ]:
3 bench presses [ jerk grip ]
3 chin pull-ups  [ w/ weight ]

3 sets: 
3 deficit parallets strict HSPU [ OR NEGATIVE PHASE ] 
1 legless RC [ from the floor ] + 1 rope climb

blocks.name: STRENGTH ENDURANCE
exercises:
EMOM 12 min | 3 rounds:

1 min: 15/12 cal row
2 min: 15/12 cal ski
3 min: 15/12 cal Echo / Assault bike
4 min: REST

- REST UNTIL RECOVERY -

STRENGTH ENDURANCE | 3 sets:

18 V-ups
14 m HS hold / 4 wall walks
10/8 C2B pull-ups
14 m HS hold / 4 wall walks
18 GHD sit-ups / 18 V-ups
- 2 min rest in between sets -

- REST UNTIL RECOVERY -

EMOM 12 min | 3 rounds:

1 min: 15/12 cal row
2 min: 15/12 cal ski
3 min: 15/12 cal Echo / Assault bike
4 min: REST

blocks.name: SUCCESSORY WORK:
exercises:
3-4 sets:

10 DB INCLINE bench presses [ SLOW down / normal speed UP ]
10 vertical block behind the neck [ w/ pause in BOTTOM position ]
